text: Václav Zavázal (born 10 February 1921) is a Czech former sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Czech male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Czechoslovakia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Příbram District
